_sText:
This is my first map, so don't knock me too hard.  I know things are wrong as far as lighting and blending of ground textures, but I don't know how to do that stuff quite yet.  It's a fun little aim map and I hope it can be enjoyed by all.  Any questions just ask me! :)

I named it aim_freestall_beta2 because I wanted to keep the original in case I get really good with mapping and want to transform it into a bomb map as well.
